# The Local Business Manifesto

We believe in the power of the local business, a demonstration of the heart and soul of a people who care deeply about the community they inhabit.

They are a people who refuse to settle for anything but the best, who make it their daily mission to enhance the lives of their comrades.

They are a people who live generously, giving not only of their time and money, but also of their wealth of wisdom and breadth of experience.

They are a people who live to change lives, who see the world not only through the eyes of numbers and profits, but also through the eyes of family. They see their employees not as servants to be dictated but as sons and daughters to be trained, equipped, and empowered.

They are a people who insist on innovation, whose willing embrace of risk continually opens economic doors to the people around them.

They are a people who rise early and work late, working with unending commitment and dedication to make sure their customers, their vendors, and their employees are taken care of.

They are a people who stare defeat in the face, battle discouragement, fight against setbacks, and yet choose to get up day after day...because they have a mission to fulfill.

These are the entrepreneurs who, though they serve in a small community, live with a big dream, a big vision, and a big heart.

It is in these hands and upon these shoulders that the future of our community rests.

We are the change.
